sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human User
    participant A as Agent
    participant AS as Auth Server
    participant R as Resource Server

    H->>A: 1. Grant permission

    rect rgba(192, 86, 33, 0.1)
        Note over A: Trust Boundary
        A->>A: 2. Create JWT Assertion<br/>(sub=user, act=agent)
    end

    A->>AS: 3. Token Exchange Request<br/>grant_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:token-exchange<br/>subject_token=JWT

    AS->>AS: 4. Validate Assertion<br/>Verify signature, claims, actor

    AS-->>A: 5. Access Token<br/>(scoped, time-limited)

    A->>R: 6. API Request<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}

    R-->>A: 7. Response
